ZH: 他们坐卧铺去了北京。
EN: They took a sleeper train to Beijing.

ZH: 你订了卧铺票吗？
EN: Did you book a sleeper ticket?

ZH: 在卧铺上你可以躺着休息。
EN: You can lie down and rest on the sleeper.

ZH: 明天的卧铺票已经卖光了。
EN: All sleeper tickets for tomorrow have been sold out.

ZH: 我们要在卧铺上度过整个晚上。
EN: We will spend the whole night on the sleeper.

ZH: 卧铺车厢里空间比较狭窄。
EN: The sleeper compartment is relatively small.

ZH: 坐卧铺比坐硬座舒服。
EN: Sitting on a sleeper is more comfortable than sitting on a hard seat.

ZH: 他们是在卧铺车厢认识的。
EN: They met in the sleeper compartment.

ZH: 我们的卧铺车厢有空调。
EN: Our sleeper compartment has air conditioning.

ZH: 你要提前去卧铺车厢排队。
EN: You need to line up early for the sleeper compartment.

ZH: 买卧铺票需要提前预订。
EN: It is necessary to book sleeper tickets in advance.

ZH: 过夜火车上有舒适的卧铺。
EN: There are comfortable sleepers on the overnight train.

ZH: 我们的卧铺车厢有独立的卫生间。
EN: Our sleeper compartment has a private bathroom.

ZH: 卧铺车厢的床比较宽敞。
EN: The beds in the sleeper compartment are spacious.

ZH: 你可以在卧铺上看书或者休息。
EN: You can read or rest on the sleeper.

ZH: 我昨天晚上坐卧铺去了上海。
EN: I took a sleeper train to Shanghai last night.

ZH: 妈妈买了三张卧铺车票。
EN: Mom bought three sleeper tickets.

ZH: 我们在卧铺车厢分开了睡觉。
EN: We slept separately in the sleeper compartment.

ZH: 卧铺车票相对于硬座来说更贵。
EN: Sleeper tickets are relatively more expensive than hard seat tickets.

ZH: 他们携带大量行李上了卧铺车。
EN: They brought a lot of luggage onto the sleeper train.
